# Naming policy

**Goal:** Names reveal role at a glance — consistent across Cursor, Claude, and Antigravity.

## Folders

| Location | Convention | Example |
|----------|------------|---------|
| App routes | `kebab-case` | `online-courses`, `[...slug]` |
| Route-private | `_components` (underscore prefix) | `contact/_components/` |
| Component groups | `lowercase` single word | `layout`, `ui`, `sections`, `seo` |
| `lib/types/` | `camelCase.ts` domain file | `navigation.ts`, `schema.ts` |
| `sanity/schemaTypes/` | `camelCase.ts` = `_type` name | `homepageSettings.ts` |
| Scripts | `kebab-case.mjs` | `check-urdu.mjs`, `run-next.mjs` |

No `utils/`, `helpers/`, or `misc/` — name by domain (`paths.ts`, `contact.ts`).

## Files

| Kind | Convention | Export |
|------|------------|--------|
| React component | `PascalCase.tsx` | default export **same name** as file |
| Lib / sanity lib | `camelCase.ts` | named exports |
| Config | `kebab-case` or framework default | `next.config.ts`, `eslint.config.mjs` |
| Schema type | `camelCase.ts` | `export const course = defineType(...)` |
| Route entry | `page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`, `route.ts` | App Router fixed names |

One primary component per file. Co-locate tiny subcomponents in same file only if private and <30 lines.

## TypeScript symbols

| Symbol | Pattern | Example |
|--------|---------|---------|
| Props | `type ComponentNameProps` | `type HeroSectionProps` — never bare `Props` |
| Domain DTOs | `PascalCase` + `Doc` / `Data` suffix | `CourseDetailDoc`, `SiteSettingsDoc` |
| Props / locals | `camelCase` | `siteSettings`, `breadcrumbItems` |
| Booleans | `is` / `has` / `should` prefix | `isOpen`, `hasChildren` |
| React components | `PascalCase` function | `export default function Footer()` |
| Constants (config) | `SCREAMING_SNAKE` | `SITE_URL`, `REVALIDATE_SECONDS` |
| Tailwind bundles | `TW_` prefix | `TW_SECTION_TITLE` in `lib/tailwind.ts` |
| Brand tokens | `dq-` CSS prefix | `dq-gold`, `dq-navy` in Tailwind theme |

Prefer `type` over `interface` unless declaration merging is required.

## Functions & methods

| Prefix | Use | Location |
|--------|-----|----------|
| `get*` | Cached Sanity/data readers | `sanity/lib/fetchers.ts` |
| `safeFetch` | Low-level GROQ with null fallback | `sanity/lib/client.ts` |
| `fetch*` | Page-level orchestration | `lib/cmsPage.ts` |
| `resolve*` | Fallback chains (SEO, contact, paths) | `lib/seo.ts`, `lib/contact.ts` |
| `build*` | Construct structures (nav, JSON-LD items) | `lib/navigation.ts`, `lib/paths.ts` |
| `nodeIsActive` | Nav active-state check | `lib/navigation.ts` |
| `handle*` | Client event handlers | `"use client"` components only |
| `generate*` | Next.js metadata/static APIs | `generateMetadata`, `generateStaticParams` |
| `urlFor` / `ogImageUrl` | Sanity image builders | `sanity/lib/image.ts` |

No vague names: `data`, `info`, `temp`, `doStuff`. Spell out domain terms.

## GROQ

| Item | Convention | Example |
|------|------------|---------|
| Private fragments | `SCREAMING_SNAKE` | `COURSE_FIELDS` |
| Exported queries | `camelCase` + `Query` suffix | `courseBySlugDeepQuery` |
| Query params | Match GROQ `$name` | `{ slug }` for `$slug` |

## Sanity schema

- `_type`: camelCase singular — `course`, `siteSettings`, `contactSubmission`
- Field names: camelCase — `featuredImage`, `seoTitle`
- Slug field: always `slug` with `{ current }`

## Abbreviations (allowlist only)

OK: `dq`, `cms`, `og`, `llm`, `nav`, `faq`, `seo`, `pt` (Portable Text in comments)

Spell out: `homepageSettings` not `hp`, `testimonial` not `testi`.

## Renames

When renaming for consistency: update imports, fetchers, queries, and types in **one change** — run `preflight`.
